title: #77 - Alex Jones Stream Shut Down
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we TRY to discuss Alex Jones- but are abruptly kicked off of YouTube mid stream and have a strike added to our account! Lovely! So instead we discuss THAT, as well as Ajit Pai's big lie, Ethan's trip to the fertility clinic, and Ian the Intern presents a power point on Lil Uzi Vert's legal trouble with the survivors of The Heaven's Gate cult!
